' ----- Configuration
'Chip Settings.
#CHIP 18F25Q10, 32

'' -------------------PORTA----------------
'' Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
'' IO:    ---------------------------------
''-----------------------------------------
''

'' -------------------PORTB----------------
'' Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
'' IO:    ---------------------------| O |-
''-----------------------------------------
''

'' ------------------PORTC-----------------
'' Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
'' IO:    ---------------------------------
''-----------------------------------------
''

'*****************************************************************************************************
'Main program commences here.. everything before this is setup for the board.

'set port DIRection as output
Dir portb.0 Out

Do
    'wait for 1 second
    Wait 1 s
    'Set the port bit to NOT (invert the current value) value from previous value
    portb.0 = NOT  portb.0

Loop
